[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":1234},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fother\u002F20230307\u002F1852899605\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fother\u002F20230307\u002F1852899605\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fother\u002F20230307\u002F1852899605\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fother\u002F20230307\u002F1852899605\u002F":1210,"related:\u002Fother\u002F20230307\u002F1852899605\u002F":1219},"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2023\u002F03\u002F07\u002Ffrontend-mock-api-with-mockoon\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":1193,"date":1194,"description":25,"extension":124,"lang":1195,"meta":1196,"navigation":167,"path":1197,"readingMinutes":1198,"seo":1199,"standalone":1200,"stem":1201,"tags":1202,"tldr":1207,"updated":1194,"url":1208,"__hash__":1209},"content\u002F雜談\u002F前端開發者不能不會的-Mock-API-技巧，就用-Mockoon-來達成吧！.md","前端開發者不能不會的 Mock API 技巧，就用 Mockoon 來達成吧！","1852899605",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":1180},"minimark",[11,19,23,26,30,38,41,44,50,55,60,63,67,70,81,86,94,97,103,106,112,116,119,498,501,506,509,515,518,524,527,532,539,543,546,552,555,558,564,568,571,577,580,593,596,599,605,608,614,617,622,625,631,635,638,643,647,650,656,659,663,666,672,675,681,685,688,694,697,702,705,709,712,865,868,874,877,883,886,890,903,910,1007,1010,1103,1106,1112,1115,1147,1156,1160,1163,1170,1173,1176],[12,13,14],"p",{},[15,16],"img",{"alt":17,"src":18},"Mockoon","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fmockoon\u002Fhp-hero.png",[20,21,22],"h2",{"id":22},"前言",[12,24,25],{},"對於一個前端開發者來講，不論是你資深會資淺，其實我個人都非常建議要了解如何使用 Mock API，而這一篇文章我會主要介紹我開發上常用的 Mock API 工具，也就是 Mockoon，所以接下來就讓我們一起來看看吧！",[20,27,29],{"id":28},"為什麼要學-mock-api","為什麼要學 Mock API",[12,31,32,33,37],{},"Mock API 的其實是在指「",[34,35,36],"strong",{},"模擬 API","」的意思，為什麼去模擬 API 呢？這邊我們來稍微舉例一下實際的開發狀況好了。",[12,39,40],{},"假設今天有一個功能開發需求是需要前端與後端一同開發的，而這個需求只有七天可以實作，但是後端卻告知你他需要 5～6 天時間才有辦法生出 API 給你串接，接著你評估了畫面切版以及要串接的 API 數量可能也要 5～6 天，那麼問題來了，身為前端的你，真的有可能等後端都把 API 開出來才去做串接嗎？",[12,42,43],{},"當然不可能，因為串接 API 的過程必定會有一些問題存在，所以串接 API 過程你還要與後端持續溝通，例如：API 打不到、屬性缺少等等，這種狀況下絕對會趕不上專案的死線，更不用說我們開發完畢後都必須盡可能預留 1~2 天作為測試的時間",[12,45,46],{},[15,47],{"alt":48,"src":49},"需求死線","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FNyJk7JL.png",[12,51,52],{},[15,53],{"alt":48,"src":54},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FJSdWq4X.png",[12,56,57],{},[15,58],{"alt":48,"src":59},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FCgEEAc6.png",[12,61,62],{},"所以如果你知道如何使用 Mock API 的話，你就可以請後端優先先開出 API 規格給你，例如：API Url、API Method、API Request 參數、API Response 等等，然後再依照 API 規格轉換成 Mock API，這樣你就可以在切完畫面後，馬上接著開始串接 API，而後端則可以專注於開發 API，這樣其實是達到一起開發的效果，也不會發生前端一直在等後端開出 API，所以 Mock API 的觀念其實是一個很好的開發模式唷。",[20,64,66],{"id":65},"mockoon-是什麼","Mockoon 是什麼",[12,68,69],{},"Mock API 是一個概念，而要做到這個觀念的工具非常多，例如：Postman、Mocky、MockServer、Mockoon 等等，而這一篇我將會主要介紹我在開發上常用的 Mockoon 這套工具。",[12,71,72,73,80],{},"首先我們進入到「",[74,75,79],"a",{"href":76,"rel":77},"https:\u002F\u002Fmockoon.com\u002F",[78],"nofollow","Mockoon 官方網站","」下載並安裝 Mockoon，你只需要依照自己的作業系統及喜好方式下載安裝檔案，並且安裝即可。",[12,82,83],{},[15,84],{"alt":17,"src":85},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fmockoon\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202023-03-07%2016.00.26.png",[12,87,88,89,93],{},"(下載網址：",[74,90,91],{"href":91,"rel":92},"https:\u002F\u002Fmockoon.com\u002Fdownload\u002F",[78],")",[12,95,96],{},"下載完之後，你可以先打開 Mockoon，因此如果你是初次使用的話，你的畫面應該會像這樣",[12,98,99],{},[15,100],{"alt":101,"src":102},"Welcome new Mockoon user","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fmockoon\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202023-03-07%2016.17.21.png",[12,104,105],{},"接著只需要按下「Start using Mockoon」，你就可以開始使用 Mockoon 囉~",[12,107,108],{},[15,109],{"alt":110,"src":111},"開始使用","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002Fmockoon\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202023-03-07%2016.20.46.png",[20,113,115],{"id":114},"mockoon-的使用","Mockoon 的使用",[12,117,118],{},"雖然 Mockoon 官方本身有提供預設的 Demo API 參考，但是我們要來實際練習一輪，所以就讓我們來假設情景吧！舉例來講，我是一位後端，然後我給了你 TodoList 的 API 規格文件",[120,121,126],"pre",{"className":122,"code":123,"language":124,"meta":125,"style":125},"language-md shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","# 名稱：取得 Todo 列表\n## API Url: \u002Fapi\u002Fv1\u002Ftodos\n## API Methods：GET\n## API Request：無\n## API Response：\n\n[\n  {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"title\": \"Todo 1\",\n    \"completed\": false\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": 2,\n    \"title\": \"Todo 2\",\n    \"completed\": true\n  }\n]\n\n---\n\n# 名稱：新增一個 Todo\n## API Url: \u002Fapi\u002Fv1\u002Ftodos\n## API Methods：POST\n## API Request：\n\n{\n  \"title\": \"Todo 3\",\n  \"completed\": false\n}\n\n## API Response：\n\n{\n  \"message\": \"新增成功\"\n}\n\n---\n\n# 名稱：編輯一個 Todo\n## API Url: \u002Fapi\u002Fv1\u002Ftodos\u002F:id\n## API Methods：PUT\n## API Request：\n\n{\n  \"title\": \"Todo 3\",\n  \"completed\": true\n}\n\n## API Response：\n\n{\n  \"message\": \"編輯成功\"\n}\n\n---\n\n# 名稱：刪除一個 Todo\n## API Url: \u002Fapi\u002Fv1\u002Ftodos\u002F:id\n## API Methods：DELETE\n## API Request：無\n## API Response：\n\n{\n  \"message\": \"刪除成功\"\n}\n\n","md","",[127,128,129,138,144,150,156,162,169,176,182,188,194,200,206,211,217,223,229,235,241,246,252,257,263,268,274,280,285,291,297,303,309,314,319,324,329,335,340,345,350,355,361,367,373,378,383,388,393,399,404,409,414,419,424,430,435,440,445,450,456,461,467,472,477,482,487,493],"code",{"__ignoreMap":125},[130,131,134],"span",{"class":132,"line":133},"line",1,[130,135,137],{"class":136},"s-VM4","# 名稱：取得 Todo 列表\n",[130,139,141],{"class":132,"line":140},2,[130,142,143],{"class":136},"## API Url: \u002Fapi\u002Fv1\u002Ftodos\n",[130,145,147],{"class":132,"line":146},3,[130,148,149],{"class":136},"## API Methods：GET\n",[130,151,153],{"class":132,"line":152},4,[130,154,155],{"class":136},"## API Request：無\n",[130,157,159],{"class":132,"line":158},5,[130,160,161],{"class":136},"## API Response：\n",[130,163,165],{"class":132,"line":164},6,[130,166,168],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":167},true,"\n",[130,170,172],{"class":132,"line":171},7,[130,173,175],{"class":174},"sMAXC","[\n",[130,177,179],{"class":132,"l